What to say, ‘Baba’, how people waste energy.

00:04:51.256 --> 00:04:57.789
Shri Krishna has said in our Gita,
“Yoga Kshemam Vahamyaham”.

00:04:57.820 --> 00:05:04.550
This means, “Yoga first.” He could say “Kshem”
first but he said “Yoga” first and then

00:05:04.550 --> 00:05:14.210
“Kshem”. “Kshem” means your wellbeing, your

00:05:14.210 --> 00:05:23.100
But first “Yoga” should take place. Until Yoga
happens, you have no business

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:31.570
with the divine. First, you should experience
Yoga i.e. union with Almighty,

00:05:31.570 --> 00:05:37.210
Atma [Spirit] should awaken within you.
When the Spirit is awakened within you,

00:05:37.210 --> 00:05:41.530
then you enter into the domain of Almighty in reality.
Otherwise, just like a crammer parrot,

00:05:41.530 --> 00:05:46.090
everything remains superficial. Until you
know your inner Self,

00:05:46.090 --> 00:05:51.150
until you have recognition of Self,
you do not enter the domain of

00:05:51.150 --> 00:05:56.990
Almighty. That’s why you are not authorised
to get what Almighty has said.

00:05:56.990 --> 00:06:01.670
Many people put blame on Almighty that we
are so much devoted to God, doing so much worshipping,

00:06:01.670 --> 00:06:06.290
we stand upside down on our head so long, we do this, do that,

00:06:06.290 --> 00:06:12.581
we offer food [bhog], morning till evening keep
chanting, but still why don’t we find Almighty?

00:06:12.606 --> 00:06:17.570
Reality is that in order to talk to Almighty,
you must establish a connection with Him.

00:06:17.630 --> 00:06:24.070
Until one attains Yoga, Kshem is not possible.

00:06:24.070 --> 00:06:29.150
‘Kshem’ means ‘your protection from all sides’,
Lakshmi Tatva [element] gets awakened within us.

00:06:29.150 --> 00:06:34.350
Krishna just said “Vahamyaham – I will do”,
But He did not explain, “How.”

00:06:34.410 --> 00:06:40.400
So let me explain to you how it works out.

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:48.223
When Yoga takes place, Kundalini rises up from
triangular bone and pierces through Brahma Randhra

00:06:48.256 --> 00:06:56.495
When the power of Kundalini pierces through
Brahma Randhra, it gets Light/flame [Jyoti]

00:06:56.520 --> 00:07:02.360
in it, because it receives Light/flame (Jyoti) of our
Spirit and due to this light, Lakshmi Tatva in Nabhi chakra

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:07.820
is awakened. As soon as Lakshmi Tatva is awakened,

00:07:07.820 --> 00:07:17.090
you will see that from all sides you will get prosperity.
If someone becomes very rich, whom we call

00:07:17.090 --> 00:07:23.210
wealthy, it’s not necessary that he would be prosperous
too. Generally the rich people are seen unhappy.

00:07:23.210 --> 00:07:28.510
More money they have, more stupid
they would be, and accordingly in their homes

00:07:28.510 --> 00:07:34.910
all sort of dirty things like wine, cunningness,
lies etc. is seen with them.

00:07:34.910 --> 00:07:38.950
All the time afraid, fears that the government will
come and catch them, may confiscate, that our

00:07:38.950 --> 00:07:44.510
money may be lost, this happens,
that happens. So, those who are wealthy,

00:07:44.510 --> 00:07:50.150
they too are not Lakshmipatis. Because
Lakshmi Tatva is not awakened within them,

00:07:50.150 --> 00:07:55.506
they have just earned money. For them money is
just like mud, it does not give any happiness.
सिर्फ पैसा कमा लिया, पैसा उनके लिए मिट्टी
जैसा है, पैसे से उनको कोई सुख नहीं है।

00:07:55.540 --> 00:07:58.747
Lakshmi Tatva must be understood.
Last time, I had explained how

00:07:58.771 --> 00:08:02.446
Lakshmi has been formed, She has two lotuses
in her hands, which are of pink colour.

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.800
With one hand, she donates and
with another gives shelter.

00:08:08.870 --> 00:08:13.830
Pink colour represents “Love”. If a human
does not have love in his heart,

00:08:13.830 --> 00:08:19.310
he cannot be Lakshmipati. His house should be
like a lotus flower. Lotus

00:08:19.310 --> 00:08:24.370
even gives shelter to an insect called “Bhanwra”,
because thats very dry, it’s sharp spikes would pinch

00:08:24.370 --> 00:08:29.110
if you keep it on hand, comforts it and
let’s it rest on its glory.

00:08:29.110 --> 00:08:33.770
Make it sleep, gives peace. Lakshmipati is
the one whose heart is

00:08:33.770 --> 00:08:39.630
Quite great. One who is very delightful to his
guests and to anyone is

00:08:39.630 --> 00:08:43.670
Lakshmipati. But you see, most of the rich
people are the greatest

00:08:43.670 --> 00:08:46.790
beggars. If you visit their house, they would die of fear that my

00:08:46.790 --> 00:08:51.110
two paisa would be spent. The person,
who is always worried that

00:08:51.110 --> 00:08:54.350
today 4 cents on this, 2 cents on that is getting
spent, save this, where to save,

00:08:54.350 --> 00:08:58.330
from where to recover, such a person
cannot be Lakshmipati.

00:08:58.330 --> 00:09:01.806
A miserly person cannot be Lakshmipati.

00:09:01.840 --> 00:09:04.890
One who is miser is a miser,
he is not Lakshmipati.

00:09:04.923 --> 00:09:09.073
A miser is poor, very poor.
He has no royalty in his behaviour.

00:09:09.100 --> 00:09:13.273
One who has no royalty in his attitude,
should not be called Lakshmipati.

00:09:13.300 --> 00:09:18.000
जो आदमी बादशाही होता है, वो चाहे गरीबी में रहे चाहे अमीरी में रहे, वो बादशाह ही होता है।
One who is royal always lives in a royal manner
either in poverty or affluence.

00:09:18.090 --> 00:09:21.430
He lives like a king. One who is worried about
petty things, after every penny,

00:09:21.430 --> 00:09:25.350
About two-two coins,

00:09:25.350 --> 00:09:30.710
cannot be a Lakshmipati. Since Lakshmi
Tatva is not awakened,

00:09:30.710 --> 00:09:34.490
he gets a strong catch of Nabhi Chakra.
Materialism creeps in such a person,

00:09:34.556 --> 00:09:39.030
he becomes very materialistic. He picks on
every small thing like this is mine, this is my

00:09:39.030 --> 00:09:43.010
son, blah blah. If all such things get in someone,

00:09:43.010 --> 00:09:45.790
he is not a Lakshmipati.

00:09:45.823 --> 00:09:49.206
“Should I steal this person’s thing, steal
that person’s thing,

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:54.873
take this or take that, everything should be for
myself,” One, who thinks like this is also not a Lakshmipati.

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:58.700
One who is for others, “If I have a posh house,
how many people will be accommodated,

00:09:58.700 --> 00:10:03.320
if I have some nice things, how many people
will feel comfort. How would I

00:10:03.320 --> 00:10:07.560
welcome others, how would
I be able to help others, how would I

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:11.940
keep others in my heart?” There is no question
of helping others. One thinks that

00:10:11.940 --> 00:10:17.000
these are my own [kins], “Whatever I am
trying to do is, to help myself.”

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:20.906
Then Lakshmi Tatva is awakened in real.

00:10:20.940 --> 00:10:22.620
His face, his lifestyle has to be like a lotus,

00:10:23.740 --> 00:10:31.890
such a person should be fragrant and
unlike one who stinks with pride. One should be very humble.

00:10:31.940 --> 00:10:38.960
One should be very humble. You must have seen
Lotus that it is bent little bit

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:44.000
downwards. Lotus never stands straight;

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.423
it’s stem is always bent down a
little bit.

00:10:47.433 --> 00:10:51.023
Likewise, the lotuses
held by Lakshmiji in her hands,

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:54.873
both Lotuses have similar tenderness.

00:10:54.899 --> 00:11:02.523
While interacting with others, he talks with very
cool attitude, with joy, full of compassion, not artificial

00:11:02.580 --> 00:11:07.220
Those lotuses are not that of plastic,
but real. Such a person in

00:11:07.220 --> 00:11:13.860
reality should be like a lotus. At one hand one

00:11:13.860 --> 00:11:17.140
donations should keep on flowing and
flowing always.

00:11:17.173 --> 00:11:19.123
I have seen my father like that.

00:11:19.160 --> 00:11:22.940
He was very generous person.

00:11:23.060 --> 00:11:27.240
Always giving. If he accumulates
something in ample, he would donate.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:30.760
He would not get enjoyment, until he
donates something. If someone tells him

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:33.180
that, “Why don’t you watch out
what people are taking away?”

00:11:33.180 --> 00:11:36.060
On this he answers that, “What should
I keep watch on? Who has to give out is

00:11:36.060 --> 00:11:42.643
giving away, I am just standing in between and giving?
What to see, I feel embarrassed when people say that I am donating.”

00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:47.810
Such a wealthy peson, who does not
accumulate anything for himself

00:11:47.860 --> 00:11:51.551
but keeps distributing things to others,
keeps giving to others, in giving

00:11:51.575 --> 00:11:55.720
he gets pleasure not in receiving,
such a person is Lakshmipati.

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:59.658
Only such a person gets it and keeps giving.
One who keeps thinking of himself,

00:11:59.682 --> 00:12:03.620
“How I will be benefitted, how my children
will be benefitted, how will I get better?”

00:12:03.620 --> 00:12:09.480
such a person is not Lakshmipati, has
no grace, he is like a beggar.

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:13.600
And with other hand he gives shelter.
Whoever comes to his house, takes care with love, care him like his own son.

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:21.900
cares him absolutely like his own son.
In his house, there are servants,

00:12:22.500 --> 00:12:27.920
animals and people in his shelter,
but they all always know that he is their

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:32.340
protector. If we have any trouble, he will
help us. Even in night he will get up to help us.

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:36.840
He does it silently and does not tell,
doesn’t let them realize that I

00:12:36.840 --> 00:12:41.320
have done so much for them, did that;
He does it absolutely secretly. God is

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:47.580
Also exactly same. He is like a woman, having
motherhood as that of Lakshmi.

00:12:47.580 --> 00:12:52.020
and she stands on a lotus. Just think about it,
in order to stand on a Lotus how much simplicity

00:12:52.020 --> 00:12:57.180
one has to have, absolutely light
without putting any load on it. That person

00:12:57.180 --> 00:13:00.860
must be such that he can stand on a Lotus
and he does not put

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:05.600
pressure on anyone. He must be very humble.
Those who show off about their possessions that,

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:10.780
“We have this, that, blah blah”
cannot be Laxmipati. Mothehood

00:13:10.780 --> 00:13:16.860
Must be in him. Must have a Mother’s heart,
then we can call him Laxmipati. All these

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:22.120
are characteristics of a Laxmipati.
And when this element is awakened in you,

00:13:22.145 --> 00:13:25.890
the first thing that comes to you is the satisfaction.

00:13:25.923 --> 00:13:30.856
There is no limit of anything otherwise, you know,
as they say in Economics that “No needs are satiable in general.”

00:13:30.890 --> 00:13:36.390
Today you have this thing, so tomorrow you need
that thing, then something else and so on.

00:13:36.433 --> 00:13:40.023
आदमी पागल जैसे दौड़ता राहत है, उसकी कोई हद ही नहीं है। आज
Man keeps running like a mad, there is no end to that. Today

00:13:40.060 --> 00:13:44.006
I get this so now I need that, something else.

00:13:44.057 --> 00:13:46.775
But one achieves contentment

00:13:46.800 --> 00:13:50.660
Until he achieves contentment, cannot

00:13:50.660 --> 00:13:55.860
enjoy anything. Because contentment is
thing of present,

00:13:55.860 --> 00:14:01.160
hope is thing of future and
disappointment is

00:14:01.160 --> 00:14:06.880
thing of past. When you stand in contentment,

00:14:06.880 --> 00:14:10.300
you are fully enjoying your possessions. Otherwise,
whatever one may have,

00:14:10.300 --> 00:14:14.900
he keeps on saying, “Oh that other person has
so much. I want that thing, then why

00:14:14.900 --> 00:14:19.280
did you get this thing?” When he gets that
he again wants something else. Such a person

00:14:19.280 --> 00:14:23.480
can never enjoy his life and neither
can he ascend. Day and

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:29.580
night his eye will be only on such things.
Things which are in vain, things which are not important,

00:14:29.580 --> 00:14:35.880
things which are meaningless in life, things
which have nothing to do with joy in life,

00:14:35.880 --> 00:14:40.680
he keeping chasing only such things in life.
But first Yoga must happen

00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:44.656
then Kshem [wellbeing] follows.

00:14:44.690 --> 00:14:47.423
Here many Sahaja Yogis have accompanied me,
who have been with me in Sahaja Yoga

00:14:47.450 --> 00:14:52.750
who have been with me in Sahaja Yoga and
they have achieved it and

00:14:52.750 --> 00:14:58.270
progressed in it. They progressed
financially too, all of them A to Z.

00:14:58.270 --> 00:15:01.990
Some of them who were penniless earlier,
gained hundreds of thousands

00:15:02.015 --> 00:15:07.646
of rupees [Lacs]. We have such people too here,
who, now as we will see here

00:15:07.713 --> 00:15:12.063
For instance, these English people, they wanted
to visit India and have been thinking,”How to go”.

00:15:12.097 --> 00:15:16.506
They have money of course. They also
achieved financial wellbeing, earned lot of money

00:15:16.540 --> 00:15:19.536
and enjoyed a comfortable life.
But when they were about to travel, a firm offered

00:15:19.560 --> 00:15:24.856
to sponsor their travel since
they had done something for them.

00:15:24.890 --> 00:15:32.139
Almighty helps even in such small ways and you save so
much of money that you don’t understand what to do with that money.

00:15:32.167 --> 00:15:38.579
Earlier they used to take drugs,
drink and all sorts of things.

00:15:38.633 --> 00:15:42.933
Lot of money used to get lost in
such things. Now I notice

00:15:42.983 --> 00:15:48.633
that they have good homes, got all good things
in their homes, they listen good music, have all good hobbies,

00:15:48.666 --> 00:15:52.273
started living a good life,
their children became very good.

00:15:52.307 --> 00:15:55.973
I asked them, “How all this happened?” They answered
that, “Earlier we used to waste all of money

00:15:56.000 --> 00:16:00.139
and had no sense about our whereabouts itself.
We were always out of our senses

00:16:00.140 --> 00:16:01.273
and had no idea about our lifestyle

00:16:01.290 --> 00:16:07.006
and actions.” That’s the reason all Gurus
prohibited wine and other

00:16:07.072 --> 00:16:13.523
such things. This wine is such harmful thing that
the moment bottle enters the house from one side,

00:16:13.557 --> 00:16:19.506
Shri Laxmi immediately steps out from other.
It’s so simple. No sooner she notices bottle coming in

00:16:19.530 --> 00:16:22.662
the house, she leaves immediately from other side.
Such person never gets blessings of Lakshmi ji.

00:16:22.686 --> 00:16:27.612
Those, in whose homes drinks are prevalent,
will never have blessings of Lakshmi ji.

00:16:27.636 --> 00:16:31.762
Of course, they may have lot of money, their sons would
waste money, wife would run away, children would run away

00:16:31.802 --> 00:16:39.108
something or other show will happen.
Tell me about one single home,

00:16:39.136 --> 00:16:47.040
where they drink, and have happiness. They cannot be
happy, as wine is always against the happiness.

00:16:47.140 --> 00:16:51.806
That’s why Gurus said “No” to wine.
Specifically, why did everyone prohibited?

00:16:51.830 --> 00:16:58.906
We must think about it. After all they were not insane.
Thousands time they told not to drink,

00:16:58.940 --> 00:17:02.473
“Drinking is bad! Don’t drink, don’t drink, ”

00:17:02.506 --> 00:17:08.529
Wine is a thing, God never created for drinking.

00:17:08.563 --> 00:17:11.913
It was created for polishing, doing polish.

00:17:11.933 --> 00:17:14.563
But people will start drinking and offering,
what to say about people’s mind?

00:17:14.580 --> 00:17:19.229
What can one do, if they start drinking anything?
Man’s mind is so stupid

00:17:19.253 --> 00:17:22.353
that anything they like, start drinking it.

00:17:22.433 --> 00:17:28.173
Who told them to drink? When you drink
this polish on the name of wine,

00:17:28.190 --> 00:17:33.140
all your lever, intestines

00:17:33.164 --> 00:17:37.164
get polished too. Even your arteries
get stiffened with polish.

00:17:37.188 --> 00:17:45.173
Arteries become so stiff that their
