third one too. That’s how this happening

00:34:13.410 --> 00:34:18.150
takes place and man gets the
light within. Now getting light

00:34:18.150 --> 00:34:22.510
Does not mean, you see the light. This is
also very weird thing that people

00:34:22.510 --> 00:34:27.930
want to see the light. When it’s about seeing
something, you are not there. For example,

00:34:27.930 --> 00:34:31.750
understand if you are outside,
you can see a building but when

00:34:31.750 --> 00:34:38.270
you have entered the building, what will you see?
Nothing at all! Then only you are there.

00:34:38.270 --> 00:34:43.203
You don’t see; Wherever one sees something,
must think that you are still outside.

00:34:43.236 --> 00:34:47.450
Those who see the light, it’s like
getting short circuited, like

00:34:47.450 --> 00:34:51.870
The light of spark, so, whoever see the light, tell me, Agnya

00:34:51.870 --> 00:34:57.350
chakra has problem. It needs to be fixed.
Your all chakras, your Kundilini

00:34:57.350 --> 00:35:02.330
cures by itself. She is your mother,
everyone’s individual mother. One that

00:35:02.330 --> 00:35:08.110
