and she ascents by itself, and

00:35:08.110 --> 00:35:11.810
cures you and takes you up
there. If you have any faults,

00:35:11.950 --> 00:35:14.470
It can be understood too,
She informs about that defect

00:35:14.470 --> 00:35:17.810
too that cure it. If you have done any
mistake, that also can be corrected.

