villagers who are simple and connected

00:38:11.250 --> 00:38:15.230
with God, they get it very easily.
They don’t take even a second.

00:38:15.230 --> 00:38:19.270
They don’t take even a second!
But in city people

00:38:19.270 --> 00:38:23.710
due to the environment and their life style,

00:38:23.710 --> 00:38:28.850
people change themselves, they go
down in their ‘Dharmas’ so much.

