That for business one has to drink. One who wants to deceive himself,
no one can save such a person.

00:38:56.470 --> 00:39:01.690
no one can save such a person. You know my husband. He has been in government

00:39:01.690 --> 00:39:05.330
job. He ran a big shipping corporation and
after that he has reached very high

00:39:05.330 --> 00:39:09.045
positions. Always, ever I have been telling him only one thing drinking is

00:39:09.080 --> 00:39:13.146
beyond me and whole life he even
did not touch it, not even a drop.

00:39:13.180 --> 00:39:15.013
And by grace of almighty, he has been very successful.

00:39:15.033 --> 00:39:17.246
Everyone honours him, respects him.

00:39:17.263 --> 00:39:20.863
Till date, has there been even a single statue
of a drunker for this was a great drunker?

00:39:20.896 --> 00:39:26.779
Tell me, any one person, in any country. In England people
drink so much. I never saw any such person’s statue there

00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:30.296
being worshipped for how much he used to drink.

00:39:30.346 --> 00:39:35.373
Has any drunker got any recognition
in this whole world anywhere?

00:39:35.410 --> 00:39:37.423
Then how can your business prosper with its help?

00:39:37.450 --> 00:39:39.990
If your reputation gets lost, how your business will grow?

00:39:40.090 --> 00:39:45.770
Business is rewarded for your repute, business is
not done for cheating. If a man stands once

00:39:45.770 --> 00:39:53.430
anywhere, people recognize him and say such a
man is there. Why are you mixing yourself in these issues of

00:39:53.430 --> 00:39:56.640
society, these illusions?

00:39:56.670 --> 00:40:02.770
You take care of your own personality.
God resides within you. In these Times

00:40:02.770 --> 00:40:07.890
It’s foolish to talk on these lines and
saying itself is foolish. But you don’t

00:40:07.890 --> 00:40:12.423
know how much have you broken yourself within,
how much pushed yourself into slavery.

00:40:12.456 --> 00:40:18.740
After getting away with such things, what is that I can grant you?

00:40:18.770 --> 00:40:24.950
You only tell me. Not at the least,
you must take a vow that, whatever we are

00:40:24.950 --> 00:40:27.356
we have self-respect.

00:40:27.373 --> 00:40:32.286
God Almighty has evolved us from
amoeba to human. One tiny amoeba,

00:40:32.310 --> 00:40:37.990
developing it into human being, how difficult it is?
After letting you pass through thousands of yonis,

00:40:37.990 --> 00:40:42.689
God Almighty has created such beautiful humans.

00:40:42.773 --> 00:40:50.414
Then he granted you the freedom to make
the choice of goodness or perversion.

00:40:50.439 --> 00:40:54.350
You can embrace anything you like. Do you
want to embrace perversion? Go get pervert.

00:40:54.350 --> 00:41:01.350
If You want to embrace goodness, be good. Now
one must think that the God who created us,

00:41:01.350 --> 00:41:06.150
with so much effort, must have built-in within us some arrangement to

00:41:06.150 --> 00:41:11.870
know him, understand him. Know self and understand the purpose of self

00:41:11.870 --> 00:41:16.890
and why we are born in this world, what is our fulfilment?

00:41:16.915 --> 00:41:21.456
Humans never tried to know why we are born in this world?

00:41:21.490 --> 00:41:28.123
Why don’t scientists think that why
amoeba was evolved into human?

00:41:28.172 --> 00:41:33.098
What’s so greatness within us for which
God created us with so much effort

00:41:33.123 --> 00:41:38.090
and granted us complete freedom. Only at this point,
even God surrenders before you since

00:41:38.090 --> 00:41:42.490
you are free. God cannot take
away your freedom. If you have to be settled in

00:41:42.490 --> 00:41:46.870
the Kingdom of God, to be adorned like a king,
then how can you be in bondage?

00:41:46.870 --> 00:41:51.856
Should hypnosis be used on you?

00:41:51.939 --> 00:41:54.939
You are completely free. If you like,

00:41:54.980 --> 00:42:00.763
embrace God in your life or
if you wish, go for Satan.

00:42:00.830 --> 00:42:05.546
God has opened both options for you completely.
And everyone has worked so hard.

00:42:05.613 --> 00:42:12.600
Let me tell you all Gurus have faced so many troubles for you.

00:42:12.600 --> 00:42:17.200
All incarnations, Gurus have put in so much of efforts.

00:42:17.200 --> 00:42:23.750
How much we tortured them, how much we cheated them. They tolerated all those pains in order to establish you, people.

00:42:23.780 --> 00:42:29.440
But this Kali Yuga came like a
typhoon that we forgot everything. And

00:42:29.440 --> 00:42:35.556
We have forgotten all our spiritual insensibility,

00:42:35.597 --> 00:42:43.023
So surprising, that we can not recognize anyone
by his face whether he is a real one or fake.

00:42:43.056 --> 00:42:50.806
If a person is Godly, it becomes evident from his face.

00:42:50.856 --> 00:42:56.230
We lost this ability to recognize [truth], that

00:42:56.230 --> 00:43:00.089
sensitivity within us completely vanished.

00:43:00.173 --> 00:43:05.330
When Rama came in this world, all knew that he is an incarnation. When Krishna came,

00:43:05.330 --> 00:43:10.889
all recognized him as an incarnation. But now
such Time has come that none recognizes anyone.

00:43:10.956 --> 00:43:13.910
In Christ Time also the same thing
happened. But few people

00:43:13.910 --> 00:43:18.070
Did recognise; But today time has come that people
recognize bhoots and rakshasas

00:43:18.070 --> 00:43:22.906
as an incarnation.

00:43:22.939 --> 00:43:26.873
One must pull out from these illusions and
one must ask for only one thing that,

00:43:26.890 --> 00:43:31.189
“O Lord, please be awakened within us. So that we can know ourselves.”

00:43:31.240 --> 00:43:36.356
Without recognition of Spirit, we cannot know God, can’t know, can’t know.

00:43:36.390 --> 00:43:40.840
Everything else is futile. All this is a circus.

00:43:40.864 --> 00:43:46.690
All these, as we call them are external

00:43:46.720 --> 00:43:52.523
displays. No point in satisfying ourselves with these external shows.

00:43:52.556 --> 00:43:56.880
You are deceiving yourself only. Who
can deceive God? He very well,

00:43:56.880 --> 00:44:03.500
knows you. You are causing losses to yourself only.
You must achieve it since it’s your own

00:44:03.500 --> 00:44:09.580
energy, your own property. The source is right
within you. Everything is filled inside you only,

00:44:09.580 --> 00:44:13.306
you must get it and then must
establish yourself in this.

00:44:13.373 --> 00:44:18.980
When I come in Sahaja Yoga, many people come, but all here say, “ Mother!

00:44:18.980 --> 00:44:21.680
They don’t make progress”.
Now, where I have seen such

00:44:21.680 --> 00:44:26.320
hopeless people but they have reached great heights.
And those, we thought great about some people,

00:44:26.320 --> 00:44:32.100
they are sticking where they were. They come back
with same issues, same headaches, same problems,

00:44:32.100 --> 00:44:34.980
same troubles. This is happening, that’s happening;
Still their level has risen only this much.

00:44:34.980 --> 00:44:42.430
In Sahaja yoga, until you give out,
you cannot progress.

00:44:42.430 --> 00:44:48.523
You will have to give out. As you keep giving to
others, you would keep progressing further.

00:44:48.556 --> 00:44:53.080
If we build a big boat, say a
ship and we don’t put it

00:44:53.105 --> 00:44:57.847
