00:45:06.410 --> 00:45:11.890
That light it and you place it under a table? The candle is light up so that others

00:45:11.890 --> 00:45:15.990
may get the light.

00:45:16.000 --> 00:45:19.665
With this you can see inside you as well others too

00:45:19.690 --> 00:45:23.890
You can see; You can see your own
Chakras and other’s Chakras too

00:45:23.890 --> 00:45:28.110
You can see your own joy and see other’s grief too.

00:45:28.110 --> 00:45:32.430
And you can know how to give it out to others,

00:45:32.430 --> 00:45:40.406
where is it getting obstructed, how should we make it.

